snippet.textDisplay:
As a '90s kid, this hit me right in the feels 💔🔥
Grew up watching the rise of Pakistan’s music scene.
EP, Noori, Jal, Aaroh, Call — what a golden era!
Seeing Laaree Chootee live again like this… man, we lived through the peak. Thank you, Coke Studio, for bringing that magic back 🙌🇵🇰❤

snippet.textDisplay:
You left… but my heart is still stuck at the place where you said your final goodbye.
Without you, everything feels incomplete—these breaths, this time, this entire life.

Every day, I wait for just one message, just one call…
where you say, ‘I want to come back.’
But whether you come back or not,
my love will never fade.

Because you weren’t just my girlfriend…
you were my habit, my prayer, my dream.
And no matter how many lifetimes pass,
I’ll keep loving you the same—forever.
Even if you forget me,
I’ll keep waiting for you…
till my last breath
love you forever bacha 🌸
